[I] Graph Theory IDE

[T] Rocs is a Graph Theory IDE for designing and analyzing graph algorithms. It
[T] provides an easy to use visual editor for creating graphs, a scripting
[T] engine to execute algorithms, and several helper tools for simulations and
[T] experiments. Algorithms are specified in JavaScript.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/rocs/

